    specialAbilities: "Devaronian Wanderlust: Male Devaronians are driven by an instinctual compulsion to roam. Labria has been running from his past for years and knows how to disappear into a crowd.\n\nFugitive Status: Labria is wanted on his homeworld for crimes including murder. He keeps a low profile and avoids any attention from Imperial authorities.",
