    specialAbilities: "Medical computer scomp link: interfacing with an adequate medical computer or surgeon droid adds +2D to all medical skills. Medical diagnostic computer and sensors. Analytical computer and sensors. 20 light manipulator arms. One main manipulator (grasper, replaceable with specific tools). Surgical attachments. Hypodermic injectors (4D stun). Medicine dispensers. No vocoder (standard); expansion slot allows addition of one.",
