    capsule: "Lieutenant Nyrox is a graduate of Raithal Academy — the most prestigious Imperial Army Training Academy in the Core — where he trained with all manner of Imperial Army hardware. His preference above all was the AT-AT walker. During an inspection tour at Raithal, General Veers witnessed Nyrox's skill firsthand in a full-immersion holo-simulation: even after a lucky hit crippled one of his walker's legs, Nyrox ground the bearings to the hub, settled into a defensive posture, and forced the Rebel simulations to come to him — destroying each one. Veers appointed Nyrox pilot of Thunderer One, the lead walker of his Thundering Herd squadron, granting him a lieutenant's rank straight out of the Academy. For his actions at the Battle of Hoth, Nyrox was promoted to Captain.",
