    specialAbilities: "Starship Intuition: Duros are very capable starship pilots. At character generation, a Duros may place only 1D in the following skills but receives 2D: archaic starship piloting, astrogation, capital ship gunnery, capital ship shields, sensors, space transports, starfighter piloting, starship gunnery, and starship shields. This bonus also applies to specializations.",
    forcePoints: 0,
    darkSidePoints: 0,
    characterPoints: 8,
