    capsule: "A tall Vuvrian with an almost comical face, Wioslea is a disarming personality — her physical appearance greatly relaxes customers, allowing her to cleverly drive hard bargains. No one knows where she comes from, and she won't talk about it. She had been on Tatooine for a few months before she approached Unut for a job, and she has served well since then. Unfortunately, she has gotten into debt to one of Jabba's con man cronies for over 1,000 credits, and thus she is quietly spying for the crime lord. Friendly but intensely private, she doesn't tell anyone any more about herself than she has to. Her objective is to pay off her debts and then relocate to another planet.",
