    capsule: "The Mos Eisley militia can call on up to 50 individuals to take up arms against Tusken Raider attacks or other dangerous situations. The militia building houses a large weapons vault (Moderate security to pick the lock; walls and door have Strength 7D) containing about 25 blast vests, 50 blast helmets, 50 blaster carbines, several dozen grenades, a score of stun batons, spare power packs, and three E-Web blasters. In times of high crisis, militiamen perform patrol duties but have been known to actively avoid action if possible. If they do become involved, they are likely to arrest visitors and allow locals to escape punishment — no one wants to arrest their neighbors. At least one militiaman is always on guard duty with a comlink to raise the alarm. The militia uses the Dewback Stables to store its vehicles.",
    source: "WEG40069 Galaxy Guide 7: Mos Eisley p.44"
