    equipment: "Lucky Despot Hotel, criminal network",
    capsule: "A young, towering and intimidating Whiphid. The daughter of two gangsters, Valarian achieved a criminal record early. Once her parents were put behind bars, she was freed to run away and really start moving into the big leagues. Her latest gamble — opening the Lucky Despot under Jabba's nose — is paying off. He is leaving her alone to pursue her interests, which include finding out what Jabba is up to. Being the second-best crime boss on Tatooine doesn't bother Valarian; she knows she will soon assume a larger throne. She has a positive attitude, has always succeeded in her varied interests, and enjoys the company of droids, treating them as equals. Her objective is to destroy Jabba the Hutt and take over his business.",
