    capsule: "Armanda Durkin is the wealthy CEO of Notsub Shipping Company — easily the largest company on Tatooine, employing almost 1,000 beings and 300 droids. She has a penchant for brocade and silks. When disguised as the pirate 'Duchess,' she tucks her auburn hair under an aviator cap and hides her figure in a flight jumpsuit. Driven by tragedy — her husband was injured and their business destroyed in a mysterious fire, and insurer Maltsett refused to pay, costing him his life — she began pirating her own shipping convoys to make Maltsett pay. She purchased the armed freighter Vengeful Sandstorm and began hijacking Notsub corvettes, selling stolen cargo at profit while claiming insurance. Her piracy turned Notsub around financially, enabling diversification and legal profits. She has grown worried — her piracy may be revealed, and a recent incident where twelve cargo haulers died over smuggled Rebel medicines has troubled her conscience. Notsub also owns Notsub Security, one of the largest private security firms in Mos Eisley, and controls stock in over 50 companies.",
