    capsule: "Thrung is a Ho'Din who has bound his ample violet locks to his head and wears a cap. His height can be intimidating to those unfamiliar with his species' natural gentleness. A typical pirate under Armanda's command, Thrung has been around the galaxy a few times. He is getting weary of Armanda's moral code against killing — the group has missed out on choice opportunities for increased wealth because Armanda will not allow her crew to strip passengers of their personal valuables. He has suggested to Armanda that it is time for her to hang up her pirate career, and is gaining converts among her crew. He has renounced his species' love of nature and turned all his energies toward technology.",
