    capsule: "Kaiya Adrimetrum is slim and athletic with jet-black hair, brown eyes, and chiselled aristocratic features. Usually dressed in simple technician overalls with a web belt of supplies. A widow — her husband was killed by the Empire during its occupation of Siluria III. She organized friends and relatives into a revolutionary cell and led an attack on the Imperial Governor, then was recruited by Corwin Shelvay. Young and extremely serious — never understands jokes and certainly can't tell them. Very aware of her responsibilities as a Rebel Unit Commander despite only just completing her eight-week officer training course. Her troops are doggedly loyal, which is impressive given her motley and poorly equipped unit.",
    source: "WEG40063 Galaxy Guide 9: Fragments from the Rim p.10"
