    capsule: "Lt. Davaire Colmar is tall, strong, with a jaw like a block of granite and close-cropped greying brown hair. A known deserter from the Imperial Special Training Corps — the fast-track to promotions and glory. During a coordinated assault on Dalron IV, a Star Destroyer bombardment cut off his unit's communications. His troops were overwhelmed by 2,000 armed citizens at nearly 50-to-1 odds. Wounded, he wandered for two days and stumbled across clinically-executed massacres perpetrated by Imperial forces. Unable to reconcile his training — that the military protects citizens — with the carnage, he deserted and joined the Rebel Alliance. His Imperial training makes him invaluable as a ground soldier who knows exactly what Imperial units are capable of. Extensive repulsorlift vehicle experience — can fly just about any speeder in a pinch.",
    source: "WEG40063 Galaxy Guide 9: Fragments from the Rim p.10"
