    specialAbilities: "",
    forcePoints: 0,
    characterPoints: 0,
    move: 8,
    equipment: "",
    capsule: "Horch of Kheedar was once a two-bit crimelord on his homeworld deep in the Outer Rim — doing a bit of slaving, gun-running, and loansharking. When the Empire assaulted Kheedar to protect its hydrocarbon processing facilities, his criminal empire fell to ruins. His loyal lackeys panicked during the bombardment, and before he knew it, he was face-to-face with Noval Garaint. Now enslaved by the ambitious bounty hunter, Horch is addicted to a rare and expensive spice liquor. He seldom remembers the details of his business deals, answers only to Garaint, and has no choice in his fate. He still holds court like Jabba, but all his stats have been reduced by his addiction.",
    source: "WEG40063 Galaxy Guide 9: Fragments from the Rim p.31-33"
