    capsule: "Torel Vorne is a short, dark Reussi with dark stringy hair he is slowly losing — personal vanity is 'beneath him.' His clothes are always too big for him, and he has watery blue eyes that never blink. He always wears a breath mask outdoors or when meeting someone in person. A despicable crimelord whose only concern is profit or loss on a transaction, with no thought as to what the involved goods may be. He controls Reuss VIII through organized crime, ensuring customs regulations remain fairly lax for smuggling operations to the Core Worlds. His 'organ donation policy' allows impoverished traders to forgive debts by donating organs — rates range from a few hundred credits for minor organs to several thousand for vital ones, yielding up to 25,000 credits. The surgery's care correlates inversely with the donation value (1D to 6D damage). Many traders prefer cybernetic replacements to being ended by Vorne's enforcers.",
