    capsule: "Vika Surn is the older sister and deadlier half of the Surn bounty hunting team. Tall and muscular with close-cropped hair and a vibroknife scar down her right cheek — evidence of hard conditioning. She possesses super-Human stamina and is responsible for executing all kills. Her emotional disorders may stem from early childhood — while never proven responsible for her parents' deaths in a speeder accident, she was hospitalized several times for mental anguish afterward. She continually trains, striving for the peak of physical perfection. Prone to frequent outbursts of anger against friend and foe alike, tempered only by her younger brother Alic's steadying influence.",
