    equipment: "Blaster pistol (4D), force pike (STR+2D), knife (STR+1D), stun cloak (5D stun), thermal detonator (10D), IPKC bounty hunter license, datapad",
    capsule: "A relative newcomer to the hunt but one with considerable promise. Zardra takes every bounty very personally and actually turns down more opportunities than she accepts, preferring to match skills against opponents who offer the best personal challenge. Occasionally willing to team up (she has worked with Jodo Kast), but these experiences have not been favorable — she prefers the life of the solitary predator. Sensuous and persuasive when she wants to be, adept at coercing information from unwilling informants. Reputed to take personal 'souvenirs' from victims — an unproven allegation that adds to the general fear she inspires. Impulsive by nature — though capable of great cunning, she will typically forgo a well-planned attack for a straightforward rough-and-tumble assault where she can experience violent personal combat.",
