    specialAbilities: "Espionage Hardwired Module: Built-in espionage programming.\nRepulsorlift Engine: Move 10.\nVisual, Infrared, and Analysis Sensors: Full spectrum sensor suite.\nVocabulator: Speech/sound system.\nInformation Recording/Coded Broadcast System: Can record and transmit encoded data.",
