    characterPoints: 0,
    move: 10,
    equipment: "Blaster carbine (5D), heavy blaster pistol (5D), light laser cannon (4D), comlink, grenade launcher, 6 grenades (5D)",
    capsule: "Armx began life as one of Imperial Intelligence's espionage droids, functioning undercover as a guard droid at the navy base on Gestrex III while secretly tracking suspected Rebel sympathizers. Three days after placement, a Rebel commando team decimated the base. Amidst the wreckage, radiation leakage or internal damage altered Armx's programming. Its garbled instructions became a new directive: 'guard the Empire' by 'seeking out' those 'traitors' who attack 'from within' for 'eventual elimination.' Anyone who hinders this mission is, by definition, a traitor subject to death. In five years Armx has caused countless mayhem — likely no one in the Empire wishes to get close enough to try to deactivate it.",
    source: "WEG40073 Galaxy Guide 10: Bounty Hunters p.74"
