    specialAbilities: "Blind Fighting: Can fight using melee or hand-to-hand combat when deprived of special sight visors or otherwise blinded, using smell and hearing to compensate. Ignores all normal blindness penalties.\nInvisibility: +3D to sneak.\nClaws: STR+2D damage.\nLight Blind: Can only see in ultraviolet. Must wear special visors to block other spectrum portions for 'normal' sight. If visor is damaged or lost, increase difficulty of all sight-related skill checks by one level.",
