    capsule: "Something of a walking arsenal, Illist Mandrep suffers from a particularly strong persecution complex. This insane Arcona is salt-addicted, resulting in particularly dangerous delusions. He believes 'enemies are everywhere' and has decided to 'fight back' by becoming a bounty hunter. He has managed to slide through Imperial bureaucracy with almost no scrutiny — in effect, a paranoid maniac with legal authorization to possess and use weapons. He has claimed many innocent victims, yet has managed to avoid the attention of the Imperial bureaucrats supposed to stop such dangerous individuals.",
