    forcePoints: 1,
    characterPoints: 13,
    move: 15,
    equipment: "IPKC bounty hunter license, comlink, datapad, light repeating blaster (6D), magnetic binders, medpac, neural inhibitor (5D stun), syntherope, Wookiee bowcaster (4D), 500 credits",
    capsule: "Chenlambec was once a peace-loving Wookiee far removed from galactic politics. When the Empire came to Kashyyyk, he refused to take up arms — repelled by the thought of killing even in self-defense. But the depredations grew until one night he slew an Imperial officer beating a defenseless Wookiee child. He escaped Kashyyyk by guile and cunning, taking refuge in the galactic underworld. He emerged years later with a false identity: Chenlambec, the Wookiee bounty hunter. He only accepts 'dead or alive' assignments for Rebels and escaped slaves. The Empire believes he has never brought back an acquisition alive — in reality, he helps his 'victims' escape to freedom. Famous in Imperial circles, no one has connected the mysterious deaths of several Imperial officers to the 'raging Wookiee.' Within certain circles: 'Don't mess with the Wookiee 'cause the Wookiee doesn't care.'",
