    move: 10,
    equipment: "None; all materials confiscated by bounty hunters during arrest",
    capsule: "For years a naval gunner with a taste for a raucous lifestyle and later a pirate who served under Jondrell, Pallas never gave much thought to the Rebel cause. When his eyes were opened to the Alliance's objectives, he left Jondrell. Though not willing to help his former pirate chief, Pallas retains a close friendship with the man who saved his life on more than one occasion. Recently, in his new role as a Rebel agitator and saboteur, Pallas has become re-acquainted with Jondrell and they shared his hide-out in the northern Kallistan foothills when they were forced to lie low in the face of Imperial pursuit. While Pallas will not betray his pirate friend, Jondrell would sell Pallas out if the price were right.",
