    capsule: "Magar Jaros is a small-time operator who produces an unexpectedly high-grade product. His skill with a tri-laser engraver is widely respected. Unfortunately, that is about the only skill Jaros has going for him. Mild-mannered and lacking in self-confidence, his profile suggests repeated rejection and personal humiliation. Jaros uses his counterfeiting ability to 'get back' (in some small way) at those who have scorned and neglected him in the past. TracSheet: Never stays on any one planet more than a few months at a time. Refuses to work with hirelings. Output generally limited to several thousand credits at one time. Has poor eyesight enhanced with computerized magnifocals.",
