    specialAbilities: "Emotion Sense: Emotion sense 4D+2. Kian'thar can sense the intentions and emotions of others. Begin at 2D and advance at double the normal cost (max 6D). Base difficulty Easy, +3 per meter away. Targets can resist with Perception or control rolls: every 4 points adds +1 to difficulty.",
