    capsule: "Little is known of Serimirl, not even her real name — 'Serimirl' is a Hutt term meaning 'allegiant.' Her origins are a mystery; while obviously near-Human, no one is sure of her race. Jabba installed her as head of his largest dummy corporation in the Outer Rim some eight years ago. With Jabba's death, she immediately purged her organization of potential rival sympathizers and vowed revenge against Jabba's 'Rebel murderers.' Her personal vendettas against leading New Republic members have disrupted governmental administration on several member worlds. Under her direction, members of various New Republic-allied governments have been assassinated, contributing to the rise of mutual suspicion and discontent. Refined, charming, and reportedly seductive, she is also very dangerous if crossed.",
