    equipment: "Blaster pistol (4D), datapad, 500 credits",
    capsule: "Skip tracers are privately hired location detection experts who typically specialize in tracking and retrieval of property (starships, droids, and the like), though they have been known to use their skills to trace 'missing' persons. Using knowledge of the local underworld often unavailable to the average police agent, skip tracers help locate the whereabouts of a wanted criminal, whether hiding in a dense urban jungle or on an isolated frontier world. As they are quick to point out, apprehension is someone else's responsibility.",
