    capsule: "The New Republic Security Force (NRSF) was established to enforce a common rule of law throughout the New Republic. NRSF agents have a dual role: seeking out Imperial agents actively engaged in overthrowing the New Republic, and maintaining civil order by ensuring the basic rights of all intelligent beings are protected. Many NRSF agents are ex-Sector Rangers. They are highly trained, deeply motivated, and backed by specialized skills and knowledge databases. They work in conjunction with local police departments and are routinely extended limited judiciary powers exercisable on the spot. New Republic law requires officers to provide offenders the opportunity to peacefully surrender before using force.",
