    capsule: "Captain Sarin Virgilio was a young Alliance officer when Bothan spies carrying the second Death Star plans came aboard his ship — a beat-up Corellian Gunship. Of a large intelligence team, only six Bothans survived, bringing the plans and the Emperor's personal schedule. Impressed by their bravery, Virgilio became a staunch supporter of the Bothans and Borsk Fey'lya. Now captain of the escort frigate Quenfis in Admiral Drayson's Home Guard Fleet protecting Coruscant, his loyalty to Fey'lya was shaken when events during a mission to arrest Han Solo revealed the Councilor's true nature. When Leia Organa Solo tricked Fey'lya into showing his true loyalties, Virgilio quickly moved to rectify the situation — no matter what he thinks of the Bothans, his loyalty to the New Republic was never in doubt.",
