    capsule: "Scout troopers are not deployed for front-line battle but are trained and equipped for reconnaissance and patrol missions, usually deployed atop Aratech 74-Z speeder bikes. Their specialized lightweight armor is more comfortable and maneuverable than standard stormtrooper armor, with lighter flexible padding replacing some heavier plating. The helmet's macrobinocular viewplate and sensor array constantly scan a 180-degree area, feeding data into a built-in computer that allows scouts to maneuver through forests, canyons and other terrain at top speeds while recording a continuous mission record. Scouts are usually under orders not to engage in combat — they locate enemies for heavier-armed troops. Thrawn deployed scout troopers in a search and rescue mission on the planet Myrkr.",
