    capsule: "Imperial Intel teams are conditioned to function in units ranging from three to 16 agents. Most team members are recruited from elite commando units and are used for combat-oriented missions rather than standard espionage. They operate in much the same manner as Rebel Special Operations Teams. These teams travel 'light' between assignments; equipment is requisitioned from Imperial stores near the mission site, or stolen from the nearest enemy depot. Whenever they are not assigned a mission, they often create their own, often leading to considerable enemy losses. They are implacable, incorruptible enemies.",
