    capsule: "Par'tah controls one of the major smuggling groups in the Borderland Regions, though most of her group's apparent wealth is illusion — hers is a marginal operation living above its means. A Ho'Din from the planet Moltok, she stands almost three meters tall, with an instinctive love for nature and an understanding of the benefits of technology. She examines every item her organization accumulates, always looking for some new trinket to add to her collection. She dislikes Brasck and his operatives with a passion, but maintains a friendly sparring relationship with Talon Karrde, who has offered her a place in the smuggler coalition partly to help float her money and partly because he respects her abilities. She is still in mourning over the loss of her friend Lishma, the Gotal killed by the Empire, which has cemented her desire to pay back the Empire.",
