    equipment: "Datapad, comlink, blaster pistol (4D), cigarras",
    capsule: "Niles Ferrier was considered one of the best spaceship thieves in the galaxy — it was said he could 'palm a Corellian Gunship while the Corellians are still aboard.' His typical method involved breaking into spaceport computer and comm systems to monitor security and route everyone away from target ships. He became involved in the struggle between the Empire and the New Republic when Thrawn offered twenty percent above market value for any combat-capable ship over one hundred thousand tons. He trailed Calrissian to the Coral Vanda and managed to give Thrawn what he wanted — the location of the legendary Katana fleet. Ferrier was a large, thickly built human with dark hair, a beard, ornate tunics, and a distinctive cigarra of carababba tabac and armudu spice.",
