    equipment: "Selection of false IDs, hold-out blaster (3D), 15 zenji needles (STR+3D+1 when used with thrown weapons: zenji needles specialization, otherwise STR+1D)",
    capsule: "Shada is an extremely attractive human female that many believe is Mazzic's love interest — constantly on hand, perceived as little more than decorative. In fact, she is Mazzic's bodyguard, highly trained in a variety of martial arts. She is a member of the mysterious Mistryl shadow guards, an enigmatic group of women warriors from an unknown world stamped into submission by the Empire. The Mistryls hire themselves out as mercenaries, taking any job that does not serve the Empire's interests. She wears her long black hair pulled up with lacquered zenji needles — not merely for styling, but weapons she can hurl with deadly accuracy, with sufficient force to crack some forms of battle armor. She once sent an outlaw-tech to a neural reconstruction facility for a month after he pinched her.",
