    capsule: "A Diollan ex-mercenary who served as an investigator for Naval Intelligence before becoming a Sector Ranger. During an inquest aboard an orbital base, he met drill instructor Thaffe and the two became friends. When Thaffe retired, they volunteered to become rangers together, making headlines stopping slave rings and pirates. After the ambush by Jabba's Gank Killers, Goa went berserk when they executed Thaffe, freeing himself and helping Nataz destroy the Ganks. Together they blew up Jabba's palace asteroid and, relieved of duty in the ensuing scandal, turned bounty hunter. Their partnership has proven spectacularly effective — they easily dispatched all the hunters Jabba sent after them and recycled the gear to fuel their new career.",
