    capsule: "As of his adventures on Kamar. Han and Chewie headed for the Corporate Sector, where word was they paved the landing strips in nova crystals. Arriving at Etti IV, they turned in their credits for crystalline vertex and Authority Cash Vouchers. Getting ship permits proved difficult — the Authority Waiver policy didn't make sense. What saved them was an offer from Big Bunji, who'd provide fake IDs in exchange for smuggling runs.",
