    equipment: "Enormous collection of opulent designer gowns and jewelry, hold-out blaster (3D+2)",
    capsule: "Neera Opatajji was the fourth daughter of the Duke of Opatajji. Spoiled and willful, she initially flirted with Hirken to grab attention away from her hated sisters. The reality of life as an Authority executive's wife was as lonely and painful as her previous life. Hirken's morbid fascination with gladiator droids was intolerable. Her life became even more wretched when they were transferred to the remote Mytus system — no social functions, no shopping, no recreation, and no one to impress with her impeccable fashion sense. She found herself feeling no regret when she killed Mirkovig. The disaster and her lonely lifestyle were all his fault. She only wished she'd survived to spend the inheritance.",
    source: "WEG40042 Han Solo and the Corporate Sector Sourcebook p.63"
