    capsule: "Uul-Rha-Shan was a famous gunfighter and assassin long before he came to the Corporate Sector. His career began as a youth running black market weapons on his homeworld of Tiss'sharl. The young Tiss'shar learned to kill and found that he liked it. His fame grew as he ended the lives of famous gunfighters such as Terrlarn, Neena Garnet and Meelto of Rodia. He was contacted by CSA operatives and earned celebrity status when he saved the life of the Assistant Advisory Undersecretary of Media. When Hirken offered a hefty salary for exclusive bodyguard work, Uul was happy to accept. But Uul-Rha-Shan made the fatal mistake of underestimating one Corellian's intelligence.",
