    specialAbilities: "Body Language: Trained by a Lorrdian tutor to read the moods of others by observing posture and body language (see Lorrdian entry).",
    forcePoints: 0,
    characterPoints: 3,
    move: 10,
    equipment: "Comlink",
    capsule: "Ido Glayyd is an intelligent, strong-willed and beautiful young woman who works hard at preserving the power base of her family. Even if by the Code she could never be the Mor, she was determined to take an active role in guiding the destiny of her clan and planet. After her father's sudden death, her brother Ewwen relied on Ido's advice since being recognized as clan leader. She has fended off the affections of other heirs from the clans of Tikeris, Melchett and Odoon — few seem as interested in her as in her family's holdings. She was privileged to have a Lorrdian tutor who taught her how to read body language, and she plans on using this information to help the Glayyds hold power and keep the other clans off balance.",
    source: "WEG40042 Han Solo and the Corporate Sector Sourcebook p.80"
