    specialAbilities: "",
    forcePoints: 1,
    characterPoints: 7,
    move: 10,
    equipment: "Tech tools, tool belt, blaster pistol (4D)",
    capsule: "Jessa inherited natural leadership qualities from her mother and grandmother. She's been around the insides of spaceships since she could crawl, learning more from Doc's extensive data libraries than most learn in twice as many years at school. When Doc disappeared, some panicked and suggested running — Jessa kept things going to do right by her father and all he'd accomplished. She trained techs to fly Z-95 Headhunters, cut tough deals with smugglers for spare parts, and ran the outlaw-tech operation until Han Solo stumbled back into her life. She made him pay his debts — he owed her — and Solo came through, helping rescue Doc from Stars' End.",
    source: "WEG40042 Han Solo and the Corporate Sector Sourcebook p.83"
