    capsule: "Lieutenant in the criminal faction run by Shettora, a fellow Hutt. Unlike most of his species, Puulio is generally well-liked by those in the criminal underworld. Soft-spoken, relatively fair (if a bit uncompromising) in negotiations, even-handed, and tends to avoid violence — though several who mistook his patience for weakness have never been seen again. Effectively controls the black market on Brentaal IV and has his pudgy fingers in several other Core World criminal ventures. Specializes in procuring starships — particularly starfighters and freighters — and selects quality merchandise, refusing to deal in defective goods. Known to pay refunds or replace damaged items. Often travels with an entourage of gunslingers, smugglers, and pirates who owe him favors, making him extraordinarily well-protected. 9D willpower, 8D gambling/streetwise/value/planetary systems.",
