    specialAbilities: "Martial Arts Techniques — Disarm: Successful unparried attack above Moderate disarms target (no damage). Flip: Moderate roll hurls target to ground for 3D damage (usable as reaction skill). Foot Sweep: Moderate roll trips target, must remain prone for the round. Instant Knockdown: Moderate roll knocks unparried/undodged target to ground. Multiple Strikes: Moderate roll allows second attack (3D damage). Power Block: Moderate roll blocks brawling attack and inflicts STR+1D damage (usable as reaction skill). | ARMOR — Modified Imperial scout armor: +1D physical/energy, no DEX penalty, move 20 (powersuit operations). Power suit +1D climbing/jumping and lifting. Sensor pod +4D search. Internal line-slinger (20m range, magnetic/claw grappler). Jet pack (100m horizontal/30m vertical, 20 charges, 2/round). Sealed enviro filter (2 hours, vacuum protection). Motion sensor +1D search (motion, 50m). Reflec coating +1D hide/sneak when not actively scanned. Wrist lasers (15 shots/unit, 4D damage, 3m range).",
