    move: 9,
    equipment: "Blaster pistol (4D damage), comlink, datapad",
    capsule: "Admiral Gaen Drommel was commander of one of the Empire's precious few Super Star Destroyers. His ship, the Guardian, was on station near Coruscant during the Battle of Endor. With word of the defeat and the death of the Emperor, Drommel fled to his home region, hoping to use his fleet to consolidate power into a personal empire. Very soon after Endor, Drommel and three Imperial-class Star Destroyers launched a short but devastating campaign against Rebel safe worlds and bases, using intelligence obtained by Captain Dor Reder from a stolen Rebel transport's computer. During the Battle of Tantive V, two of the three Star Destroyers were destroyed and the third, the Wolf's Claw, was captured by Alliance forces and incorporated into the New Republic fleet. Drommel escaped with the Guardian, though the ship was heavily damaged. Drommel is a fearsome and intimidating individual who commands the kind of respect that many charismatic despots enjoy — his soldiers fear him, but would follow him to their graves.",
