    capsule: "Tord Gamb is a known gambler and con man, with a long history of frauds, cons and other deceptions. Since the rise of the New Republic, there have been few reports regarding Tord Gamb, until very recently. At the shipyards of Sluis Van, Gamb managed to pose as an independent trader with supplies needed by the shipyards. After gaining access to the shipyards, he was able to con numerous targets out of a total of several hundred thousand credits. Since then, there have been reports of three similar operations on the worlds of Bimmisaari, Maphus Tria and Algarra II. It is also believed that Tord Gamb has been able to secure very detailed information regarding the New Republic defense net around Asmall. If this information were to become available to the Empire, this important manufacturing center might be lost and we cannot allow this to happen.",
