    capsule: "Jontin is Gornt Seron's lieutenant and second in command. His duties include maintaining the security of Seron's castle and commanding the castle guards. In Seron's absence, Jontin takes charge of the organization on Korbin and on other worlds. Jontin is Seron's most trusted advisor, and is privy to Seron's plans and ambitions long before those plans are even begun. When situations off world require on-site supervision, Jontin is often sent to straighten out matters on Seron's behalf. When this occurs, Jontin brings a detachment of guards and enforcers with him, usually numbering from ten to 40 men.",
