    capsule: "Mexnean is a diminutive con woman known to frequent starports, drinking establishments and other areas where it is easy to find marks for her slick con games. Mexnean's cons run the gamut, from crooked sabacc games to laundering dirty credits from spice smugglers. She has been known to pose as an employee or operative of a company or criminal and roll up a tab of tens of thousands of credits while living the good life. She then disappears before her scam is revealed. Mexnean is wanted by the Republic for questioning because it is believed that she has dealt with several prominent crime lords in the past few months. The Republic now has sufficient evidence regarding minor crimes that she could be put in prison for several decades — if Mexnean promises to reveal what she knows about the crime lords, the Republic might be convinced to overlook some of her past activities. Reward for capture: 1,500 credits.",
    source: "WEG40062 Wanted by Cracken p.83"
