    capsule: "Finn wears black pants and a lightweight flowing caftan over a long grey tunic. He has greying black hair and a scruff beard. He has a long scar beneath his right eye and always seems to have a sardonic smirk etched on his features. Little is known about Finn, save that he has a reputation for brutality and ruthlessness. He is loyal to Janelle Serap, and there is a persisting rumor about a romantic link between the two. Glacially calm, Finn is capable of rapid decisions under fire. He has a keen awareness of his abilities, and knows he can best just about everyone on Seikosha.",
