    specialAbilities: "Vision: -1D penalty for visual actions beyond 20m, cannot see beyond 40m, but +1D to Perception for objects within 30cm. Scent: +1D to Perception skills for actions and people within 3m. Manual Dexterity: +1D to fine motor skills.",
    forcePoints: 0,
    characterPoints: 4,
    move: 6,
    equipment: "None",
    capsule: "Lin has a large head and black, lidless eyes. Her mouth and nose are hidden by folds of skin. In her despair at being on Narg, she has allowed a thin layer of coal soot to collect on the pale skin of her hairless scalp. Since Biths do not sleep, she spends all day and night in the bar, sipping a green drink through a straw. When she runs out of money, she goes to the TGM deep mining station to compute stress analyses for tectonic manipulation excavators — making her the only alien directly employed by the corporation — then returns to the bar to drink until broke again. Lin is very unhappy about being trapped on Narg.",
    source: "WEG40083 Classic Adventures p.98"
