    forcePoints: 0,
    characterPoints: 3,
    move: 11,
    equipment: "Wood carving tools, grey kilt",
    capsule: "To-yel is a tall, cheerful humanoid covered with thick gray fur, wearing only a gray kilt. He has a flat, almost nonexistent nose, heavy brow ridges, and two fleshy cones protruding from the top of his head that detect electromagnetic radiation. Unlike most Gotals, To-yel has difficulty sorting through signals and feels constantly bombarded with unwanted information. Narg is a paradise to him — less electromagnetic noise than any other planet he has been on. He spends most of his time carving figurines and seldom talks.",
    source: "WEG40083 Classic Adventures p.98"
