    characterPoints: 6,
    move: 6,
    equipment: "Various tools, comlink",
    capsule: "Maytoc is a middle-aged, rather grizzled Human male. He is short, with closely cropped grey hair, and is missing his left leg. He normally wears an oil-stained engineer's coverall with the left leg sewn shut. Little is known about his background, but it is apparent he served on the Worthless Fool before it was acquired by the Rebellion, as extensive modifications were made to accommodate a one-legged person. Many believe he once worked closely with pirate Yearo Seville. Someone in the sector Imperial government was rumored to be responsible for the loss of his leg, and his involvement in the Rebellion is an attempt at vengeance. Maytoc is taciturn and inward-looking — while a skilled pilot, his real pleasure is tinkering with engines and shipboard systems.",
