    capsule: "Yearo Seville is a Human of menacing countenance. He is of average height and build, with dark hair and nine parallel scars on his left cheek. He carries a gold-plated blaster and dresses in expensive, outlandish attire. Seville's life of crime started at a very tender age — he joined up with smugglers and by his fifteenth birthday had killed his hundredth man. His cold-hearted cunning and greed led him to found his own pirate gang. He is now famous throughout Rayter Sector as the most bloodthirsty and dangerous criminal. Self-serving and dangerous, Seville cultivates an air of menace and constantly manipulates his underlings, creating a constant sense of paranoia amongst his henchmen.",
