    capsule: "Thaddeus Ross is a handsome, easy-going Corellian of 28 who comes from a long line of smugglers. A non-traditionalist, he broke free of the family legacy and became a bounty hunter, quickly gaining a reputation for capturing particularly dangerous criminal personalities. However, the notoriety wore off and he returned to the family tradition of smuggling. Despite a ruthless occupational edge, Ross is easily provoked by senseless violence. Cynical and self-righteous, he has a weakness for protecting the underdog and often interferes to even the odds. Flies the modified YT-1300 Kierra, which has a droid intelligence with its own feisty personality. Wanted by the Empire for 5,000 credits.",
