    capsule: "How and why Kierra got into the onboard systems of the light freighter are not known. She was either trapped inside the ship or hidden there sometime after its construction. Ross accidentally awakened her and thus began a long partnership with the eccentric droid. While she can manipulate certain ship functions, she had to learn astrogation and shields from her Human mentor. She continually learns new functions through self-programming. Her uncanny ability to imitate Human behavior is disarming — feisty, feminine, and possessed of unusual curiosity, heavily influenced by Ross and prolonged contact with other eccentric species.",
