    move: 10,
    equipment: "Lightsaber (5D), dark robes, comlink, transponder link",
    capsule: "Adalric Brandl is a highly intelligent, self-motivated individual whose grim obsession with tragedy stems from his career as a tragic actor on Trulalis. Even before his seduction by the dark side, he was a callous, moody man preoccupied with the next star-crossed character he was meant to play. An apathetic murderer, he kills without remorse — an invaluable resource to the Emperor. He returned to Trulalis seeking redemption from his old taskmaster Otias, but was denied forgiveness. He has a son, Jaalib Brandl, living in the Kovit Settlement with his mother. Brandl activated his Imperial transponder to summon a Star Destroyer rather than endanger his family further, surrendering himself back to Imperial service.",
