    forcePoints: 0,
    characterPoints: 12,
    move: 8,
    equipment: "Expensive clothes, sporting blaster (3D+1), various trinkets and knickknacks",
    capsule: "Slythor is a typical Squib, perhaps a meter tall with reddish-blue fur, huge blue eyes, and large ears with white tufts of fur. Well-groomed and wearing loose-fitting expensive clothes, he is the self-proclaimed 'Highest Exalted Ruler of Korad.' About three years ago, he took control of a large salvage yard on Korad, establishing himself as the planet's ruler. He enforces his rule with a fleet of 20 modified Verpine asteroid hoppers and 10 cloud cars. While not as cheerful as most Squibs, he is very egotistical, believing himself a demi-god with a grand destiny. He holds the art of haggling in the highest regard and strikes deals for both immediate gain and long-term profit. His deal with The Scourge — trading a gravity well projector for captured ships — exemplifies his shrewd business sense. His major problem is that none of his clients take him seriously.",
