    capsule: "Pelleo Thog is a successful businessman, entrepreneur, and sportsman on Torina with a fascination for rare creatures, which he collects from across the galaxy. A hobby since childhood, his collection grew proportionally with his wealth. Finally heeding his wife's complaints, he built a private zoo and garden on his immense estate with numerous outdoor enclosures and arboretums for specimens from alien environments. His zoo is his greatest treasure and he constantly undertakes expeditions to find new additions. He is also a skilled sports hunter and expert in sporting firearms and bow weapons. He is friendly with Imperial officers including Captain Dadefra of the Star Destroyer Brazen and Captain Tanda Pryl of the Thunderflare.",
