    capsule: "A fierce-eyed tall human with thinning white hair and gaunt features, Captain Hatanga is a native to Elrood sector and has flown its space lanes since he was a young lad. He believes in 'The Code of the Stars,' an old-fashioned system of ethics calling for floggings, putting troublemakers in airlocks, and other harsh discipline to keep crews in line. The hard-drinking Hatanga still believes in its principles and is eager to tell anyone who'll listen about how 'today's spacers just got no discipline.' He recently lost his captain's license and most of his BoSS permits because of a drinking problem. His ship, the Galax Titan, is an old ore carrier big enough to smuggle a light freighter inside its cargo bays using slightly radioactive ore to foul Imperial patrol sensors.",
