    capsule: "Shondra Del is known to many as a skilled tramp freighter captain, but in truth she's a top-level Rebel agent assigned to organize Alliance operations in Elrood sector. She's worked the sector for many years as a freighter captain and has a reputation as a reliable smuggler with many connections in the sector's thriving black market. Shondra is responsible for establishing Rebel cells, securing supply sources, and negotiating deals with potential allies. She supplied goods to the Friends of Paran resistance fighters on Derilyn and eventually brought them into alliance with the Rebellion. She made contact with the Khuiumin Survivors pirates led by Jacob Nive, but ISB agents tracked her. Captured on Torina, she resisted General Hul's interrogation droids and was sentenced to die in his Arena of Games.",
