    equipment: "Command rank cylinder, datapad, comlink, blaster pistol (4D)",
    capsule: "Captain Alistar Dadefra is a driven man who commands the Imperial Star Destroyer Brazen. Now 53, the highlight of his career was as captain of the Victory-class Star Destroyer Bombard when he engaged the Eyttyrmin Batiiv pirates in the Khuiumin system, decimating their fleet of 275 ships. Recently assigned to Elrood sector to eliminate pirate activity, he has also been encouraged to stifle the rivalry between Captain Akal Zed of the Stalker and Captain Tanda Pryl of the Thunderflare. He insists Super Star Destroyers are 'parade ships' and prefers real action. The Khuiumin Survivors, led by Jacob Nive, nearly destroyed the Brazen in a brutal ambush — the crippled ship now undergoes repairs at the Derilyn Space Defense Platform. Dadefra is determined to find and destroy the pirates forever.",
