    equipment: "Sporting blaster: Galinolo XX, Diplomatic Edition (3D)",
    capsule: "Dr. Nardah is a small, wizened Human male with worn skin and stooped shoulders. His silver hair still grows thick, and he has not lost any of the vitality of his youth. He dresses well, as befits a diplomat, in the conservative fashion of the Old Republic, and the blaster he wears, while underpowered, has been constructed of the finest materials. His primary motivation as a member of the Alliance Diplomatic Corps is to prevent primitive sentient races from becoming slaves of the Empire.",
