    characterPoints: "",
    move: "10",
    equipment: "Expensive gray suit",
    capsule: "Darryn Edalm is a tall, thin Human with pale skin and red hair. He is a low-level bureaucrat — paranoid and compulsively meticulous — who is trying to fit the mold of sophisticated Imperial Governor. Edalm is the Imperial researcher who rediscovered the results of the original survey of Karra, leading him to believe that there existed a large mass of valuable resources on the planet. He shared this belief with his superiors and was granted the Imperial Governorship of Karra as a reward. Unfortunately, his reward soon turned to shame when the miners discovered there was no varmigio on the planet. All civilian personnel were recalled, and after the military commander determined the natives were not a threat, the majority of military forces were withdrawn. Suddenly, Governor Edalm had control, but no power — and no importance.",
    source: "WEG40138 Classic Adventures Vol 4"
