    equipment: "Datapad, holdout blaster (3D+2), comlink",
    capsule: "Jerik Snivas is a small, stoop-shouldered man with greasy, receding hair and shifty eyes. Born on Lianna, he joined the Imperial Office of Criminal Investigations (IOCI), where he worked as an investigator for many years. Success in several smaller matters brought him an important posting at Kwenn Space Station, where his ability to make deals and gain contacts soon made him a major player in the local IOCI office. After years of conniving and dealing, Jerik was caught in a few shady matters and left the IOCI to become a licensed expediter. His intense personality coupled with his nonstop chatter often clinches deals where a more subtle approach would bog down. Jerik is out solely for himself — all information has value, and he is a master at trading it. He manages to cover his utter selfishness and lack of loyalty with charm and fervent intensity, but at heart he'd do anything for a fast credit.",
