    capsule: "Daralla Errine is the owner of the CrossWind Saloon on Seregar. She is tall and attractive, but maintains a no-nonsense, business-like manner. After a brief and very lucrative smuggling career, Daralla gathered a few associates and sunk her earnings into the CrossWind Saloon. Since then, she's tripled her money, partially through the saloon's business, but also through back-room deals and trades. She sees the CrossWind as becoming the center of a vast smuggling network, and intends to be on top running things in the next few years. Daralla deals honestly, believing that a relationship firmly grounded in trust results in great returns. She is an impeccable judge of character and remembers favors and returns them; likewise, she holds grudges forever.",
