    capsule: "Captured on Ryloth and sold into slavery at an early age, Lliandri managed to escape and eke out a living on the dangerous streets of Ord Mantell. She found her calling when she was forced to defend herself with a blaster. While she regretted killing her attacker, she liked the 2,000 credit reward the local authorities handed out. Lliandri is a tall, attractive green-skinned Twi'lek with dark eyes who favors a heavy armored vest and wears twin heavy blaster pistols in quick-draw hip holsters. She dresses revealingly to distract the undisciplined riffraff she deals with. Driven to prove herself and survive in a hostile galaxy, she often resorts to unneeded violence to intimidate opponents. She claims to refuse Imperial contracts because the Empire allows slavery. In truth, Lliandri is secretly working with Tern Ashandrik — her story about him stealing a bounty from her is a cover to infiltrate groups of bounty hunters and lead them into Ashandrik's ambush at the Trigdale refinery.",
