    capsule: "A proud Gamorrean, Uurk is far from the stereotype of a mindless brute. He's a proud and successful lawkeeper, with a perceptive (if beady) eye and a keen (if somewhat slow) wit. His sense of honor and justice approaches that of a Wookiee. If he ever returned to Gamorr, he would probably be ostracized for his 'gnorn' — 'cowardice,' the word closest to 'cunning, knowledge' in the Gamorrean language. Uurk knows that Narloch is corrupt, but is trapped by the laws he has sworn to uphold. He may oppose bounty hunters who blatantly disregard Emmerian law, or secretly aid those who try to work within it. His partner is a battered security droid named 'Kay' — the only droid Uurk respects, though that doesn't stop him from clobbering Kay occasionally.",
