    capsule: "Narloch of Giju is a Herglic gambler and entrepreneur. Careful to maintain a legitimate facade (even his thugs have licenses for their weapons), Narloch is actually in charge of Jabba the Hutt's gambling operations in Nilgaard sector. He owns casinos on Emmer and Reaper's World, and has interests in casinos on several other worlds. He travels frequently aboard his ship, the Elusive (a modified DuroTech Arnette-class Superluminal rapid passenger shuttle). Those who hunt him must work outside the law or outsmart him at his own game. Lord Haakon, a minor noble whom Narloch cleaned out in a high-stakes sabacc game, has placed an illegal private bounty on him.",
