    capsule: "T-3PO is a tall, silver Imperial protocol droid with a cold, angular face and large, insectoid photoreceptor eyes. It walks stiffly and carries itself with a dark sense of superiority. The opposite of C-3PO in many ways — nasty, belligerent, condescending, and speaking in a rasping female accent. It believes itself superior to all other droids and hence feels it must survive. It has served aboard the Subjugator for many years and is intimately familiar with many of the service levels and droid access chutes. While it hates humans in general due to its treatment in Imperial service, its programming remains loyal to the New Order. It joins the Rebels to save its metallic skin, but betrays their positions to stormtroopers during a zero-G battle, claiming afterward that old programming reasserted itself.",
