    move: "10",
    equipment: "Translator device",
    capsule: "Und'l is a most unusual being — a Buzchub, a species from a far corner of the galaxy. Like Wookiees, their vocal chords make them incapable of speaking Basic, so spacefaring ones equip themselves with translator devices. Somewhat stocky and covered in dark blue fur, he affects an air of always knowing more than he is telling. Once Buzchubs get used to the galaxy, they are rather urbane about it all — not terribly curious about other species or technology, they really just want to travel. Und'l hooked up with Imperial sympathizers a short time ago but thinks he's merely moving spice, unaware the cargo is actually lexonite, a deadly poison.",
