    capsule: "The King's Own Guards are an elite paramilitary squad responsible for honor duties and elite missions on Lazerian IV. Their traditions and methods go back centuries, and even today they still practice a chivalric code. Of all the Lazerian military forces, the King's Own Guards are easily the best trained and most efficient. They serve under Commander Alroy Kever, the King's trusted aide.",
