    equipment: "",
    capsule: "Milo Phineas is a short, stocky man who looks almost jolly, always with a smile that makes it easy for him to gain someone's trust — including the trust of smugglers, whom he then arrests. A retired Imperial captain now serving under Commander Sloane aboard the VSD Enforce, he firmly believes Sloane is his key to success and almost idolizes his commander. Despite his friendly appearance, Phineas is actually cold and calculating, willing to do anything to advance the status of his commander and himself. He is patient and will toy with smugglers until he gets them where he wants them. Not immune to bribery, but will never agree to anything against his commander.",
