    capsule: "Unknown to New Republic agents or even mine overseer Quarlo, Vanel was an Imperial Intelligence sleeper agent from the Destabilization branch. At odds with her supervisors over how to enslave the Kluuzot, she accepted Quarlo's offer to become his personal bodyguard and enforcer. A survivor of several assassination attempts, she is a hardened killer who prizes professionalism and works hard maintaining operations at peak efficiency. She holds no grudges but feels it is simply good business sense to deal with all who cross her. Force-sensitive — any Force users will sense unease around her, and she will know if a mind trick is attempted, taking great offense.",
