    move: "10",
    equipment: "",
    capsule: "Quarlo I'Shibix is the corrupt administrator of the Mon Tondievz mining complex on Krann. Formerly the Imperial colony administrator, he defected just hours before a court martial for corruption was scheduled to begin. He offered his colony's services to the New Republic through an exclusive deal with Mon Tondievz Mining Company, presenting himself as a reformed man who reorganized the operation and gave Kluuzot workers shares in profits. In reality, the mines are largely tapped out from Imperial overexploitation, and Quarlo secretly runs an eldratz drug operation that brings in ten times what crystals used to. He controls his Kluuzot workforce with eldratz laced with neural stimulant instead of containment collars, releasing burned-out workers back into the wild. He fabricated tales of industrial sabotage to lure patsies while planning his escape with hoarded nova crystals and eldratz profits.",
