    capsule: "Kird Telak is the founder and leader of Telak's Terrors, a pirate gang operating from a hidden underground base on Seltaya, the outermost planet in the Ropagi system. He has a huge mop of frizzy black hair, a goatee, and a slim moustache, with the look of a merry rogue. He wears expensive clothing carefully doctored to look worn and battle-scarred. A successful Imperial scout for six years until the job bored him, he took up piracy using his extensive knowledge of trade routes, ship schedules, and planetary defenses. Often called reckless, he enjoys danger and gets bored easily. He considers himself a dashing, charming rogue but would cheerfully condemn a comrade to a slow death if necessary. Wanted by both the Empire and the New Republic. Bears no loyalty to anyone and would sacrifice his men instantly to save his own skin.",
