    capsule: "A strong-willed and determined man, General Reskan is driven by his desire to see his homeworld of Bacrana and Brak sector freed from the Empire. Former commander of the Bacrana System Defense Force (BSDF), he defected after refusing to aid in Moff Ramier's violent crackdown on the Amma protest. He secretly organized a guerrilla group, funnelling military supplies while still commanding the BSDF. After fleeing to the Tel system, he established Oracle Base and eventually joined the Rebel Alliance, gaining reinforcements, equipment, and technical staff. In excellent physical condition with shoulder-length gray-streaked black hair and a relaxed, friendly manner that occasionally disconcerts others.",
