    capsule: "Byro Ti'mere is a middle-aged, black-haired computer expert who runs InfoServices, a private investigations and intelligence service specializing in obtaining and analyzing electronic information. His clients range from crimelords to corporations to the Rebel Alliance. He employs about 15 slicers who access computer networks across the sector using the best portable computers and spikes. His operation is hidden on a tiny asteroid called Brugga in the Latoma system — a decoy outpost on Latoma itself throws off pursuers. He never meets clients personally, working through lieutenants Jyss Cordam and Dav Wissark. Despite never leaving Brugga, he always dresses in stylish clothes and listens to the sector's newest music while working.",
