    capsule: "Equa Felens was born to LMC mid-level managers in the auditing division, travelling to every major world in Brak sector as a child. He enrolled in BEI's galactic government program, became politically active, and met Dara Gion. They both participated in the Amma protest where a scout walker blast wounded them both and blinded Equa. After going into hiding, they joined Reskan's group. Equa had his damaged eyes and hearing replaced with a Neuro-saav Hifold Sensory Package. Now a capable fighter and accomplished covert operative, he runs a Rebel safehouse in Brenn, Genesia. His familiarity with Brak sector's worlds makes him a competent scout and recruiter.",
