    specialAbilities: "Hypnotic Voice: extremely hypnotic voice that lulls targets into a false sense of security. +2D to con, persuasion, and pick pocketing attempts.",
    forcePoints: "3",
    characterPoints: "12",
    move: "13",
    equipment: "Two medpacs",
    capsule: "K'lial and Diskio are the last surviving members of the Khzrry family unit, once one of the most respected Xi'Dec families. The other members were killed when the Empire assassinated Senator Mael Sidras aboard the Savage Pleasure resort liner. K'lial, being somewhat more humanoid (four extra arms), takes the lead when dealing with authorities. Its expansive vocal capacities provide one of the most comforting Basic accents in the galaxy, while its arms and grasping claws weave almost hypnotic patterns — occasionally withdrawing objects from pockets and purses. 70% of rescued agents are taken directly from captors by K'lial's voice alone. On the TGM corporate headquarters infiltration on Pako Ramoon, K'lial distracted guards with an elaborate 'marriage proposal' ruse while picking locks and restraints, buying time for the extraction speeder to arrive.",
    source: "WEG40084 Cracken's Rebel Operatives p.10"
