    specialAbilities: "High Dexterity: can use eight legs for several simultaneous actions with no penalty; for manual dexterity actions, up to 3 actions per round with no penalty. Claws: each leg ends in a sharp claw, STR+1D damage. Natural Body Armor: +1D+1 against physical and energy attacks.",
