    capsule: "Reginna Bel Typolla, or 'Gina,' works as a docking attendant at the busy Fabrillan City Spaceport, checking registry datafiles on incoming and outgoing ships and filing manifests. She copies manifests, registries, and incoming ship data, leaving 'damaged' datapad disks in the trash for Sid's network to collect — though she has no idea Sid is her Rebel contact. An Alliance cell operative set the whole arrangement up over a year ago, and Sid accidentally found out her identity. A native of Malthor, she unknowingly ran guns during the Medepiest Uprising — General Cracken notes the Empire likely doesn't know of her involvement. Part of Sleeper Cell V-16.",
