    equipment: "Hold-out blaster (3D), datapad, military comlink",
    capsule: "Moff Harlov Jarnek achieved his position through hard work and effectiveness. He is a ruthless and efficient administrator who has methodically worked his way up since graduating from the Imperial Naval College. Not inherently evil, but coldly efficient — he will do whatever he deems necessary to eliminate problems. A solitary person who seems not to mind that no one has ever achieved a high position and done well at maintaining it while also having a strong desire to share that success with someone. This is why he took to having a 'pet' so easily — unknowingly, his companion Dælar vuv Tertarrnek is an Alliance deep mole whose empathic sense allows him to act appropriately no matter Jarnek's mood.",
