    move: 10,
    equipment: "Datapad.",
    capsule: "Graff Teiras is Retter Lewis's chief lieutenant — store manager and head of Callia's shipping operations aboard the Cal Ambre in the Bramior system. Teiras is a tall, imposing middle-aged man with silver hair and a barrel chest. His official duties are as liaison with shippers, sellers, other dealers, and estate auction houses. Unofficially, Teiras manages the day-to-day scheduling of pipeline movements for the Alliance defector extraction network, ensuring deliveries and pickups are set and positioned along every point. He is also in regular contact with higher-ups in the Alliance.",
