    capsule: "Salishh grew up an orphan on the streets of Devaron, stealing food and credits to survive. When he reached adolescence his tastes grew a little more expensive — what he wanted was to get off-world. He sold a few thousand HarborVacc vacupumps, which got him more than enough money to book passage off his homeworld. That he didn't own any vacupumps was the trick. With that first con he was hooked. He is not the most talented grifter ever to hop a system, but he is well-known in that community and frequently takes on apprentices, accepting any profits made during the training as payment. Among his better-known scams include selling real estate on the surface of Bespin, and trading phony shares in Tagge Industries.",
