    capsule: "The wily slicer known only as Valeress is quite good at what she does. When she was young and foolish, she broke into the Corporate Sector Authority's black operations database. CSA assassins have been on her trail for years now, and she has had several narrow escapes. She sells her talents to whoever can afford them and gain her trust, which is not easily given — she can never be sure that her client isn't on the Corporate Sector Authority's payroll. Everyone is a suspect to Valeress, including even her own family, most of whom have worked for the CSA.",
