    equipment: "'Hammer' slug-thrower (3D+1), walking stave (STR+1D), comlink, breath mask",
    capsule: "B'Yen Do V'nel is a true zealot, sincere in his belief that the gods of M'Nes will intervene on behalf of the Gorothites once they prove their willingness to fight for their freedom. He is young and charismatic, with the ability to inspire fanatical devotion in his followers. He broke away from the T'B'Dellyi'Mai to form K'Len J'Bar Kasoon ('Rightful Vengeance of the Mother'), believing that organization lacked the spiritual dimension necessary for true liberation. He preaches that the M'Nes religion's call for patient submission is a corruption of the true faith — that the gods want the Gorothites to fight, not submit. His organization is relatively small but fanatically devoted. His followers are willing to sacrifice their lives without hesitation. The Colonial Government views K'Len J'Bar Kasoon as dangerous fanatics but less of a strategic threat than the Gor'Jen'Ar.",
