    capsule: "Tere Metull is the senior Rebel Alliance operative on Goroth Prime. The Alliance's interest in Goroth is straightforward: hyperbarides are vital to turbolaser manufacture, and denying the Empire access to a major natural source would be a significant strategic coup. Metull's mission is to make contact with the resistance movements and evaluate their potential as allies. She operates under deep cover, posing as a mid-level corporate consultant. She is cautious, methodical, and patient — qualities that have kept her alive in one of the most dangerous assignments in the sector. She has made contact with the Gor'Jen'Ar and is cautiously developing a relationship with S'Ten Gali Ak'Ar. She has been instructed to avoid the T'B'Dellyi'Mai and K'Len J'Bar Kasoon as too volatile and unpredictable. The Alliance maintains plausible deniability regarding her presence on Goroth.",
