    capsule: "Mikka is second in command and chief engineer of the Roughnecks, and Lens's husband. He is 60 years old but looks younger, 1.7 meters tall with a dark complexion. Overweight but carries it well. Wears mechanic's overalls and tends to leave a trail of dropped hydrospanners and microswitches wherever he goes. When excited, lapses into a heavily-accented brogue nobody can understand. One of the few Humans who can actually speak Wookiee. Worked for the Sartran Corporation as an engineer and was imprisoned when it was disbanded. Met and married Lens in jail; when released through a clerical error, he begged, borrowed and stole enough money to purchase his wife's freedom. Basically non-political — joined the Rebellion because his wife did. Counterbalances her aggressiveness with native caution and humanity. His dream: design the best hyperspace alternator sequencing module in the galaxy.",
