    capsule: "Grizzled Human male with a sour disposition and quick temper. Raised on the industrial world Yalln, spent his youth scouting vast unsettled territories. Served briefly in the Imperial Army learning military theory but had unfulfilled aspirations of becoming a drill instructor. Joined GOSS to bark orders at impressionable recruits. Too old for Imperial service and despises the Alliance. Not a direct combat threat due to advanced age, but his resources at GOSS make him a concern. Some attributes and skills lowered to reflect aging.",
