    equipment: "Comlink",
    capsule: "Former Imperial scout who serves as Barosa Warren's personal assistant at GOSS. From the Lesser Plooriod Cluster, only son of a widowed trader. Framed by a commanding officer of having falsified reports regarding the Giryulan Findings and forced to flee Imperial space. Found haven at GOSS. Middle-aged Human with a rough countenance and aloof disposition. Seldom engages in conversation but is a knowledgeable survivalist, particularly in aquatic and urban environments. Entrusted with Warren's most important assignments and performs them flawlessly.",
