    capsule: "Callandri's older cousin and co-founder of the Granse Confederacy. Born to a prosperous trading family in the Asamin system. Worked as a smuggler for Captain Thi Sawrtin until intercepted by the Interdictor-class cruiser Tory's Catcher — Captain Gresia Vleen shot Sawrtin and imprisoned Zayl. Escaped from Imperial detention on Rol Two. Worked for Sullustan gangster Tiron Til until refusing an assignment involving Trandoshan spice smugglers, then was cast out. Reunited with Callandri and now focuses on hunting Alliance operatives. Impressive freighter pilot and blaster skills. Wanted by the Empire, ensuring she won't receive Imperial contracts.",
