    capsule: "One of the few Tunroth Hunters to have survived the Reslian Purge. Spent years as a skip-tracer hunting debt-dodgers for crimelords. Successful in every assignment. Was employed by Hutt families in the Y'Toub system until his disdain led him to spit on Glorga the Hutt — expelled but not killed, reflecting his clout. Companion Arcuse left with him. Sullen and withdrawn, considers the Confederacy his only friends but often dines alone. Uses antiquated black powder pistol and a klirun bow powerful enough to send arrows completely through stormtrooper armor. His traumatic Reslian Purge experiences have made him a bitter individual with little interest aside from the hunt.",
