    capsule: "Kerestian bounty hunter from the Tamarin sector. Formerly employed by Gotal crime lord Pari'Notgoth until falsely accused of an assassination attempt and fled. Has brought in over 30 bounties, mostly to Imperial authorities. Known for an exceptionally violent temper — once lost a sabacc hand and his ensuing rampage left one Bilar dead and caused thousands of credits of casino damage. Tall Kerestian with light yellow skin and thick brown double tails from forehead ridges. Light green eyes nearly pupil-less from an explosion at the Clariv Shipyards — vision returned but seared. Missing jagged teeth from a Gamorrean brawl. Stole the Mon Calamari freighter Waterspire from an Alliance depot on Wilpiet.",
