    capsule: "Rodian bounty hunter and only child of legendary ghestslayer Kalon Lenitor. Raised in the bayous southeast of Rodia's capital. Unlike the conceited, overeager Rodian stereotype — intelligent, refined, and a hard worker. Anchored by loving parents and a sense of community. Cast from the Swinif Organization, was gaining favor with Mid-Rim syndicates when joining the Confederacy. None of her bounties have been Rebels — mostly criminals and mercenaries. Wanted by the Alliance for questioning about the Mapuzo break-in, not for a crime. Gets along well with Callandri.",
