    capsule: "Gand findsman and second cousin of the bounty hunter Zuckuss. Currently most wanted by the Alliance of all Granse Confederacy members — possesses high-security datafiles from captured Alliance agent Patel Odfath detailing operations in the Shiwal and Cademimu sectors, potentially exposing nearly a thousand operatives. Adopted the ancient findsman ways, believing the mists guide his hunt through elaborate rituals. Formerly employed by Kian'thar loan shark Ne'lear. Believes the mists showed him to the Confederacy and intends to stay. Flies the modified Koensayr Sigma-class shuttle Mist Laden.",
