    specialAbilities: "Vision: Can see in infrared, allowing sight in complete darkness with heat differentials. Natural Body Armor: +2 bonus against physical attacks. Fangs: Six pairs of long fangs do STR+2 damage. Quills: Arm and leg quills do STR+1D+2 when brawling.",
