    capsule: "31st leader of the m'Yalfor'ac Order, a continental army of nearly 700,000 soldiers on Guiteica. Hero of the Bitthaevrian people, respected and admired for his anti-Republic rhetoric and strong leadership. Gained his position through meritorious combat, guerrilla operations against pro-Republic corporate complexes, and exceptional leadership. Has defended against several usurpers. Suffered permanent injuries in battle against the traitor Major Jael Ganton Farvash. Opposes the Rebel Alliance because it seeks to restore the Republic that defeated the Order — considers the Empire the lesser of two evils. Has no love for the Empire either and has blasted Imperial patrol craft entering Bitthaevrian space. Dark skin covered with scars from many dematoil battles. Bitthaevrian naming: Quaal = birth season, Tavier = family name, Catharius = personal name.",
