    capsule: "A former slave turned slaver — once enslaved on Hintivan II where he felled huge trees with vibro-axes for years. Somehow acquired enough credits to buy his freedom, then sold his knowledge of slave rings to the Mytaranor Slaving Council and rose to become its leader. Acquired the Mandalorian Dungeon Ship Vanquisher from Kessel, establishing a virtual monopoly in slave trade in Mytaranor space. Deals in species common in Alliance ranks — Wookiees, Mon Calamari, Bothans. Large man with thick frame, light purplish-blue complexion, black mottled arms, short black hair. Wears an old snowtrooper armor chest plate from his slavery days. Weapon of choice is the same vibro-ax he was forced to use as a slave.",
