    capsule: "A Shatras bounty hunter who only takes assignments where the target is of a reptilian species — believed to hunt out of some conviction of his species' superiority over all other reptilians. An effective hunter who has brought in scores of wanted beings and only failed a handful of times. Responsible for capturing Rebel operatives Larkor (Barabel) and Thlan-sa (Kath), and made an unsuccessful attempt on special operative Jungen. Recently tried to capture Lt. Commander Xenon Nnaksta but was beaten badly by Nnaksta's companions. Bitter rival of the Tiss'shar bounty hunter Kal-tan-shi — their rivalry threatens Alliance security as both hunters frequently target Rebel operatives.",
