    specialAbilities: "Senses: Weak long distance vision (+1D difficulty beyond 15m), excellent close range (+1D Perception for heat/smell/movement within 15m). Thick Hide: +1D STR vs physical. Talons: +1D to climbing, STR for brawling damage, or digging. Salt Weakness: Very Difficult willpower to resist addiction if salt consumed; addicts need 25g/day or -1D all actions.",
