    capsule: "Recovering salt addict and leader of the Zulirian Swordmasters. Former acquisitions director for the Zuliria Museum of Antiquities, Ancient Weaponry department. Educated at the Lerct Historical Institute where he fell into salt addiction in his second year — nearly destroyed his career. After recovery, graduated ahead of schedule. Eventually grew tired of studying relics and took a more active role. Founded the Swordmasters as an academic group that has since turned into violent vigilantes. Scholar: Ancient Melee Weapons 7D, Value: Melee Weapons 7D+2, Melee Weapon Repair 9D, (A) Metallurgy 7D. Willpower: Salt Addiction 8D+1.",
