    specialAbilities: "Cyborg body: Kligson's body is almost entirely cybernetic; requires no food or water. +2D to Strength to resist physical damage and +1D versus energy damage. Internal Blaster: blasters built into cybernetic hands (damage 5D, range 10 meters, 10 shots).",
