    move: 10,
    equipment: "Internal blasters (5D, range 10m, 10 shots), Kligson's Moon mobile space platform",
    capsule: "After receiving grievous injuries during a battle many years ago (reputedly during the Clone Wars), Kligson's damaged body was outfitted with a vast array of cybernetic parts. Witnessing the cruelty that living beings inflict on each other firsthand, the disenchanted warrior vowed never to interact with organics again. He built a massive mobile space platform — 'Droid World' — out of spare parts, surrounding himself exclusively with salvaged droids in an unexplored system. Had a brief encounter with the Empire and the Rebellion; afterward moved Droid World and has not been seen since. Will not deal with organics or choose sides in the war. May speak to characters with cybernetic limbs, but anything he repairs, he keeps.",
    source: "WEG40116 Cynabar's Fantastic Technology: Droids p.14"
