    equipment: "Snulf box, hold-out blaster (3D+2), expensive tailored suit",
    capsule: "Officially Nim Zanti's senior business and operations advisor. In reality, Zanti's keeper — a Tenloss lieutenant representing the Syndicate's wishes, monitoring operations, and providing the voice of experience in crises. Rose through Ororo Transportation's smuggling operations, transferred to Galindas Export's logistical support, and has worked in distribution departments of most Syndicate fronts. Never a smuggler himself — always a manager, riding herd on independent-minded smugglers. Completely amoral, master of carrot-and-stick management. A 1.9m tall, bald, olive-skinned human of indeterminate age with beady black eyes that rarely blink — gives the impression of a human reptile. Always accompanied by two Natori bodyguards.",
    source: "WEG40134 Shadows of the Empire Planet Guide p.37"
