    capsule: "Enjoys the immense prestige of his posting as consul-general on Bothawui. Officially charged with coordinating all Empire intelligence activities in the Both system, but usually declines to involve himself past the initial concept phase — relies on staff and daily briefings. Believes if a mission is important enough, someone will let him know. Fancies himself an ambassador of goodwill, hosting lavish parties and soirees with exotic dishes, delicate wines, and accomplished musicians playing elegant waltzes under Bothawui's three moons. An accomplished fencer. Commands 100 low-level bureaucrats, tax collectors, and 300 stormtroopers.",
