    capsule: "Handles security for Consul-General Pring's diplomatic estate — no easy job given the density of spies and saboteurs in Drev'starn. Coordinates sweeps of consulate grounds and security checks during Pring's many receptions. Has foiled dozens of attempted incursions. Also handles electronic security with a team of slicers monitoring computer systems — multiple layers protect from outside slicers but she has difficulty controlling Bothan 'moles' on Pring's staff who steal data from within. Under orders, sometimes leaks misinformation to known Rebel and Bothan spies, though she finds it distasteful — would rather round them up and interrogate them. A stern, no-nonsense officer known as 'Officer Sunshine' by her overworked staff. Hopes a good recommendation from Pring will get her a real command post.",
