    capsule: "Founder and leader of Beldonna's Legion, a 56-member mercenary company with 6 Y-wings. A confident Corellian and expert with most weapons. Fighting is what she does best and she's an inspiring leader. Runs her unit with stringent rules — misconduct not tolerated, disputes resolved in painful but non-lethal hand-to-hand duels (winner wins the argument). Enjoys her position on Kothlis but prefers more action — frequently takes her band hunting in the Arblis Forest or ice caps to stay sharp. High profile, parades proudly about Tal'cara's nightspots. 28 years old, attractive but frail-looking — well-toned muscles hide tremendous strength. Long straight black hair braided when on duty. Gilad Halsek is infatuated with her.",
