    capsule: "Belongs to Clan Ojia, one of the smaller clans on Kothlis. Was employed by MCS managing warehouse computers but resented the lowly position. Began embezzling funds and discovered the access hatch and natural caves behind the unirail power generator beneath Tal'cara's platform. Built a computer center there, tapping into the generator for power, and expanded the caverns. Now operates the largest spynet facility on Kothlis. Associate of Borsk Fey'lya — remained behind as his inside connection when Fey'lya joined the Rebellion. A young Bothan, brilliant programmer, wears plain clothes and maintains a low profile. So ingrained in computers he forgets to ripple his fur during communication — considered insulting to other Bothans, so he avoids contact.",
    source: "WEG40134 Shadows of the Empire Planet Guide p.85"
