    capsule: "This short Sullustan dispatcher works out of a complex of docking bays and warehouses in a corporate starport sector on Lianna. She routes small cargoes from the XTS depot to various destinations around the Allied Tion sector. Her chamber is in the transparisteel-enclosed dome atop the central tower, commanding a perfect view of the complex. Nuutu maintains a very professional atmosphere — all employees wear tidy XTS coverall uniforms. She personally meets with transport pilots for assignments and pay, reserving moments for idle chatter to carefully judge character. Upstanding spacers who never break the law rarely get special smuggling jobs. She can spot a weakness and exploit it, sweetening deals with spare credits and vouchers to the XTS company store. To those who cross her or the company, Nuutu can become a dangerous adversary. (XTS is a front for the criminal organization Black Sun.)",
