    capsule: "Shirro is the burly leader of the Blood Razors swoop gang on Biivren, a minor industrial world in the Expansion Region. The gang's chief purpose is to provide for the industrial sector's outcast inhabitants — trafficking black market goods and redistributing materials stolen from Imperial forces. Those within the factory area are under their protection. Shirro looks and speaks tough, but among the refugees he's known as a kind man who protects and feeds them. His main concern is keeping the Blood Razors in weapons and spare swoop parts. He always keeps a long metal pipe handy for hand-to-hand engagements, with a special sheath strapped to his swoop bike.",
