    capsule: "The well-to-do Maxeena Sov'lya is an independent investor based on the Bothan colony of Kothlis. In public she's a member of high society, a position attained through her family's shrewd, legitimate business decisions. In truth, she's left operation of family ventures to trusted subordinates — she spends most of her time running the small crime syndicate she established under her parents' noses. She runs rackets at the starport and keeps several smugglers on retainer to import or export contraband. Maxeena is rumored to have influence over Beldonna's Legion, the local mercenary security force's second-in-command. She leaves hands-on execution of illegal affairs to her distant relative, Uncle Dravos.",
