    capsule: "The dour Twi'lek woman who partners with Hawker Bryce-Kelley aboard the Royal Mistress. Always has a brooding, untrusting look about her — one hand always on her blaster. Rypka never speaks aloud, communicating entirely in the silent Twi'lek language of hand, head-tail, and body gestures. She is an alluring young woman but equally dangerous. Some say she's a fugitive from Ryloth; others believe she's an escaped slave girl. Silent as a shadow and deadly with a blaster.",
