    equipment: "Blaster pistol (4D), comlink, credit pouch, datapad, Kaal starport uniform",
    capsule: "One of Kaal's customs officers, maintaining a balance between the Imperial Customs bureaucracy and the free-traders who import luxury goods, contraband, and specialty items for vacationers on this tropical Mid-Rim world. Kaal's island cities are teeming with Imperial personnel on leave. Murahl isn't above bending the rules to make sure everyone is happy — smugglers, Imperial clients, casino and hotel owners, and her credit pouch. Most of her business comes from people paying her to ignore certain indiscretions. She's careful enough to catch those whose activities would arouse Imperial suspicion. Has declined offers to partner in larger schemes — she doesn't have the means to broker illegal cargoes and prefers keeping evidence minimal. Her pleasant attitude, warm smile, and quick inspections make any visitor to Kaal feel welcome.",
