    equipment: "Blaster pistol (4D), bulk freighter Spiteful, datapad, Nebula Consumables corporate uniform",
    capsule: "Perhaps the only corporate transport pilot who looks good in the company uniform. Captain Seprine pilots a bulk freighter for Nebula Consumables, running mundane and luxury food items to exclusive markets in the Expansion Region and Mid Rim. Like most corporate pilots, she holds free-traders and smugglers in low regard — haughty, confident, and condescending in all matters of business. Not above ratting out competitive smugglers to local authorities. Seprine enjoys manipulating others — if she seems friendly, she's probably pumping you for information, misdirecting you, or sending you on a market tip far from her territory. Her infamous romantic relationships are just as manipulative — she's had relationships with every male crew member, which is why they all obey her without question. Known to charm a spacer just to twist him to her own schemes, then toss him aside.",
