    equipment: "Blaster pistol (4D+1), secured comlink, datapad, expensive clothing",
    capsule: "Unlike most Snivvians, Knarr doesn't have an artistic bent — unless you count ruthless money-making endeavors an art. He has set up semi-permanent shop in one of the Emporium's private rooms called The Exchange. What Exovar doesn't know is that Knarr is using it as a staging ground to take over the entire Emporium, intending to use it as a base for piracy, smuggling, bounty hunting, and slaving. He is quietly bringing in mercenaries as muscle for his plot, which is nearing completion.",
