    capsule: "He stands well over two meters tall and his thick frame is wrapped in solid muscle at over 150 kilos. Gorge cuts an imposing figure, easily slipping into the role of bouncer. Despite his appearance, he isn't a mindless machine of destruction — he picks his fights carefully and would rather avoid confrontation. Though he regularly fought in the Dool Arena in the early days, he almost never enters the ring anymore. Usually found moving through the shadows, stepping out at just the right moment to discourage disturbances. Most famous for his right front tusk, the tip broken off in the crash-landing that brought the brothers to Reuss VIII.",
    source: "WEG40153 Wretched Hives p.48"
