    capsule: "A native of Coruscant born with some natural ability in the Force, but his skills are meager at best. He has turned his attention to gambling and fighting, slowly being consumed by the dark side — though he is so insignificant the Empire hasn't bothered to hunt him down. His fighting style mirrors his gambling philosophy: he will take chances if rewards outweigh danger. He wields his lightsaber in arena combat, and while his skills aren't tremendous, the intimidation factor of the energy blade is considerable. Average-looking with sparkling green eyes and silvery hair, one of the oldest contenders whose skills have not diminished with age.",
    source: "WEG40153 Wretched Hives p.56"
