    capsule: "A mysterious being who appeared unannounced one amateur night and quickly proved his incredible skills, going undefeated in 30 bouts. An honorable fighter who refuses 'cheaper' tactics — will not strike a fallen opponent and has yet to kill anyone in the Arena. Quiet both in and out of the ring, with a soft, mellifluous voice. Pale, almost chalky skin with long ebony hair, electric blue oval pupils against black backgrounds, a silvery sigil weaving around his neck and royal purple tattoo above and below his left eye — he refuses to discuss either. Enjoying a growing fan base, especially among female customers. Unknown to all, Brin is a Nagai, a humanoid warrior race from a remote star cluster beyond the borders of the Empire.",
