    capsule: "One of the most feared inhabitants of Wildwater. No good ever comes of his presence — when he appears, someone else vanishes. Began his criminal career as an enforcer, eventually coming to Odanni's attention. Specializes in assassinations with exotic poisons derived from Calamari's flora and fauna. When he walks the halls of Wildwater in his dark cloak, a large path is cleared. Something of an urban legend — no one knows who he works for, but he's widely suspected of being an assassin. Enjoys taking the doomed out for one last submersible ride to Rako's Rift, a deep-sea trench home to the terrifying krakana.",
    source: "WEG40153 Wretched Hives p.78"
