    equipment: "Biotech Borg Construct Aj^6, 'Geneering RiMPack, Neuro-Saav cardio-muscular package, Neuro-Saav Hifold sensory package, Neuro-Saav Hi-Sense enhanced eyes, upgraded galven BlasTech integrated (left arm) A280 blaster rifle (7D), Vec-Tech integrated (right arm) concussion missile launcher (9D)",
