    capsule: "Blizz Pinnix cuts an impressive figure — or he would if anyone knew what he looked like. Racing for over 40 years, no one has ever seen his face. A debate still rages over what species he is — most agree probably male, though never proven. Never seen without his signature racing helmet in holo-photos, souvenirs, or anywhere else. Since he owns The Pits, no one is sure when he's personally in attendance. Once in a rare while, the intensity of races leads to the arrival of a rider dressed in solid black on the infamous ebony Black Raptor — and every racer knows the stakes have gone supernova.",
