    capsule: "Semler Tevez grew up in the culture of the Kanauer Corporation. His father, Jeoff Tevez, is director of the Thrugii mining division near Socorro. A talented pilot, Semler graduated from the Imperial Academy with high honors. Using his family influence and credits, he was released from military duty to pursue a more profitable career in mining. He now supervises one of the main Thrugii camps, but whenever the Kanauer territorial lines are challenged, Semler dons his flight gear and personally defends company boundaries, using the same single-minded determination of his Imperial TIE pilot counterparts. Immaculately manicured and well-groomed, Semler wears the Kanauer uniform with pride. It is rumored that he handles worker revolts and trespassers with the same ruthless ire he shows in space battles.",
