    capsule: "100-150 men are on security duty throughout Soco-Jarel Spaceport at any time. They are well-armed and permitted to use their weapons to prevent or quell disturbances. Treachery is not tolerated on Socorro, where fair treatment among one's peers is expected and, in most cases, demanded. When trouble rears its head, there are normally an additional 20-30 smugglers in the area who will happily join in the fun.",
    source: "WEG40154 Black Sands of Socorro p.21"
