    capsule: "Caelli-Merced techs are hand-picked for their skill and credentials — the finest mechanics in Socorran space. Just about every modification is available, from customized smuggling compartments to extremely efficient shield generators and sensor stealth systems. Turret mounts can be hidden away to avoid nasty questions from Imperial or sector authorities. Repairs are expensive and one-of-a-kind modifications come at an even higher price — several cargo loads of spice may be in order to pay for a single modification. The work is first-rate and exceptionally reliable. Techs are always on the lookout for new talent — anyone showing skill and willingness may get an offer to join this exclusive group.",
