    equipment: "Flowing white robes, hold-out blaster, datapad",
    capsule: "Dr. Uth Sulrowe is a Mon Calamari antiquities appraiser who runs The Emporium, an exquisite boutique in Cjaalysce'l for rare items unavailable elsewhere in the galaxy — even on the black market. Dressed in flowing white robes, she is a vivacious hostess, offering drinks and pastries as she points out key pieces of interest. A shrewd dealer and business-minded individual, she personally checks out each customer with an excellent sense for who can pay and who can't. Her intuitive senses have seen through several Imperial infiltrators hoping to expose Pret Swain's operation. The Emporium has a reputation as something of a museum, but everything in it is for sale. Trusted patrons may be invited to see 'truly rare' pieces in the back room — actually a tubelift leading to an underground access tunnel where a small landspeeder whisks them away to the manufacturing center, an isolated bunker under the starport where they can peruse rows of Caelli-Merced blasters or try out swoop racers and land vehicles.",
