    specialAbilities: "Berserker Rage: +2D Strength for brawling damage when enraged, -2D to non-Strength actions. Climbing Claws: +2D climbing.",
    forcePoints: 3,
    darkSidePoints: 3,
    characterPoints: 10,
    move: 10,
    equipment: "Modified bowcaster (5D), comlink",
    capsule: "Kuykenda is a Wookiee of enormous size, presence, and strength — and equally intimidating temper. As Pret Swain's personal friend and bodyguard, this overly opinionated Wookiee is second-in-command of the Caelli-Merced organization. A former Imperial slave (freed by Swain when he captured a slave galleon in the Ottega sector), Kuykenda has learned much in the way of interrogation and torture, and enjoys putting those skills to the test — particularly on captured Imperial infiltrators. Kuyk is arrogant, abrupt with strangers, and generally indifferent to anything not directly related to Caelli-Merced's success. His brusque behavior is indulged by Swain due to his affection for the powerful Wookiee. In his spare time, the Wookiee enjoys wrestling with monnoks — at least 10 of these creatures guard the limited access areas of Swain's well-secured fortress. He is the eldest of seven brothers including Rakikta, Cjaalysce'l Starport's security manager.",
    source: "WEG40154 Black Sands of Socorro p.47"
