    capsule: "Squig is the mechanical mastermind who maintains Badawzi's vehicle and freighter fleet. The Jawa's advice is often sought by Caelli-Merced technicians. Much to Halbert's horror, Squig has taken to making impromptu repairs and modifications to the Seldom Different without telling him — and often at the worst of times, such as when Halbert is running from Imperial patrols or in the middle of a battle. Squig makes it a personal challenge to keep Halbert's ships spaceworthy no matter how badly the smuggler abuses them. He can repair even the most extensive damage, though his chaotic methods and odd mannerisms draw comment from observers. Where Squig and Halbert go together, disaster and mayhem are certain to follow. A true romantic, hardy adventurer, and chronic gambler, Squig has taken a liking to Halbert and his comfortable life in Badawzi's monarchy. Squig can often be found in his home away from home — the abandoned engine casing of a bulk freighter hidden somewhere in the dungeons of Badawzi's underground hangar. An avid story-teller, the Jawa enjoys relating his star adventures to anyone who will tolerate his high-pitched voice.",
