    capsule: "S'oelle Khiss is the nephew of Sluissi chancellor Secies Uslopos, Abdi-Badawzi's right-hand henchman. A promising lackey himself, S'oelle is slated to take his uncle's place in case of Secies's untimely termination by the ill-tempered Twi'lek monarch. When Secies is out performing on Badawzi's behalf, S'oelle often runs the court and has fortified his position in the crime lord's good graces. An idealist, the young Sluissi has transcended the corrupt morals of his environment and yearns to serve under the famous Mon Calamari hero Ackbar. In a chance meeting with the Mon Cal, S'oelle voiced his praises and support for the Rebel effort — and was given an assignment to keep contacts open between the Rebel Alliance, Badawzi's crime network, and the Black Bha'lir.",
