    capsule: "Grenal is more than just the chief security officer of Neftali — he is also the tribal and spiritual leader of the Whiphids who live here. A shaman born on Toola, the Whiphid homeworld, Grenal earned the prestigious title of Spearmaster shortly after his arrival on Neftali. He is an intimidating presence as he patrols the multi-tiered docking arena at Cordel Cove. As one of the most successful hunters on Neftali, Grenal is in high demand as a guide into the frozen wilderness. The 34 Whiphids of Cordel Cove are loyal to Memcha but take direction from Grenal, who is in turn respectful of Syychi above all others.",
