    capsule: "Kara Reenogga is well-known for her fiery temperament and stubbornness. Among the three Reenogga sisters, Kara is perhaps the easiest to find — she loves to frequent Chabak's at the Hub, out-drink the patrons, challenge newcomers to tests of unarmed combat, and gamble. She has befriended the Twi'lek Quink at Chabak's; the two try to outdo each other in exchanging colorful insults and barbs, and Kara enjoys helping out by throwing around customers who are bothering younger Padda. One of three identical triplet sisters running Reenogga Personal Services Cubed (RPS Cubed) from the Death Mark on Zirtran's Anchor.",
