    characterPoints: 12,
    move: "10",
    equipment: "Comlink, datapad, 6 fragmentation grenades (5D), heavy blaster pistol (5D), vibro-axe (STR+3D), weapons harness",
    capsule: "Sully Tigereye served with the Rebel Alliance, enlisting as a standard ground force trooper. He worked his way slowly through the ranks, gaining the attention of superiors and fellow soldiers as a fearsome warrior prone to exuberant fits of violence. He eventually caught the eye of Colonel Andrephan Stormcaller, who had him assigned as fire support coordinator for the infiltrator team designated Red Alpha. He directly participated in nearly every Red Alpha mission since. When Stormcaller left the New Republic military — displeased with their handling of the situation with his homeworld of Entralla — Sully Tigereye and a handful of other infiltrators joined him to form the Red Moons. Although shorter than a Wookiee, the bristly brown-furred Trunsk has shown he is more than proficient with heavy blaster rifles, repeating blasters, vibro-axes, and other large weapons. Two shiny sharpened tusks protrude from his lower lip; he was once treated like an animal in a carnival ring fighter show, an experience that left him with a deep hatred of slavery. He led the Red Moons strike team that liberated the Karazak slaving operation on Gabredor III.",
    source: "WEG41008 Star Wars Adventure Journal #8 p.183"
