    specialAbilities: "Invisibility: Adds +3D to sneak. Claws: Adds +2D to damage when brawling. Light Blind: Defel can only see ultraviolet light and must wear light visors to screen out other forms of light — without a visor the difficulty of any sight-based task is increased by one level. Force-sensitive.",
